dct_title_s: State of Utah : Compiled from the official records of the General Land Office and other sources
dct_description_sm: Relief shown by shading, hachures and spot heights.; Includes legend. Shows state capital, public survey offices, district land offices, county seats, cities, towns and villages, county & land district boundaries, national parks, monuments, bird reservations, Indian reservations, bureaux of reclamation projects, military reservations.
dct_publisher_sm: U.S. Dept. of the Interior General Land Office (Washington,  D.C)
